title: 8.91-111013a-126818E-ATI.7z
description:
new AMD complete leaked driver package for Vista/Win 7 both version only.
8.910...
catalyst 11.11 beta preview or rc ?
Difficult to say anyway.
However without any release note and or changelog and no more information about this last one.
Looks like a beta/rc/whatever of 11.11... looking at it now:

These drivesr are dated from october 13 and therefore are more recent than catalyst 11.10 preview 2 release
but a little bit older than the very newest catalyst 11.10 preview 3 dated from october 16...
A bit troubling so anyway...
Btw this complete driver package for Vista/Win7 both version only includes several very interesting stuff as :

1)Intel Graphic switchable products driver support with complete Intel media sdk components.
(nice interesting complement)

2)complete SBDrv driver package for AMD mobo chipset including AMD Filter,hseries,SB4xx,SB6xx,SB7xx,SB8xx,SMBus,SMBus-svr
including AHCI,RAID drivers and much more again.(very usefull anyway)

3)complete driver package for AMD video cards indeed,with display driver,OpenCL,hdmi driver,wdm,hydravision,AMD media component,AviVo,CCC,ect...
